short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Rediret tabs' proxy in current open window

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Redirects URL of all tabs in current window to another proxy.

Steps to use:

1. Click on the green arrows on the right upper corner.
2. Select reload.
3. Wait for all pages to be reloaded with different proxy.
